        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued July 21 at 3:57PM CDT until July 21 at 4:15PM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 357 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 10 miles north of
Pampa, moving northeast at 25 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to roofs, siding, and trees is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Skellytown.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
